## Note for Next AI

> **This system uses a fake payment worker for testing. The `PAYMENT_MODE` secret switches between `fake` (calls fake-omise worker) and `live` (calls real gateway). To change the live gateway, only modify the `if (paymentMode === 'live')` block in `order.js` and the corresponding webhook handler. Do not change the fake mode block.**
